    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="meta">Effective Date: June 18, 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Last Updated: June 18, 2026</p>

    <p>HoldOff ("we," "us," "our," or "Company") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our Service at shouldiholdoff.live and our mobile applications.</p>

    <hr>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

    <h3>1.1 Information You Provide Directly</h3>
    <p><strong>Account Registration:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Name, email address, phone number (for SMS/contacts sync)</li>
      <li>Password (hashed and encrypted — never stored in plaintext)</li>
      <li>Mental health condition selections (optional, used for personalized insights)</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Communication Data:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>SMS messages and their content</li>
      <li>Contact names and phone numbers</li>
      <li>Message timestamps, metadata, and conversation history</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Subscription &amp; Payment:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Payment method information (processed via Stripe — we do not store full card details)</li>
      <li>Billing address, purchase history, and subscription status</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>1.2 Information Collected Automatically</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Device type, OS, browser type and version</li>
      <li>IP address and approximate location</li>
      <li>App usage analytics and interaction patterns</li>
      <li>Session cookies and authentication tokens</li>
    </ul>

    <hr>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Deliver core messaging and conversation features</li>
      <li>Provide AI-powered insights and coaching responses</li>
      <li>Process subscription payments and manage your account</li>
      <li>Send transactional emails (confirmations, password resets, billing)</li>
      <li>Debug, improve, and secure the Service</li>
      <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
    </ul>

    <hr>

    <h2>3. How We Share Your Information</h2>
    <p><strong>We do NOT sell your personal information.</strong></p>
    <p>We share limited information with trusted service providers:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Anthropic (Claude AI):</strong> Message content is sent to their API for AI analysis. Anthropic processes this per their own privacy policy. We do not use your data to train AI models.</li>
      <li><strong>Stripe:</strong> Payment data for subscription processing (PCI-DSS compliant).</li>
      <li><strong>Render / Cloud Infrastructure:</strong> Hosting and storage (encrypted in transit and at rest).</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We may also disclose information if required by law, subpoena, or court order, or to protect the safety and rights of our users.</p>

    <hr>

    <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>All data transmitted is encrypted via HTTPS/TLS</li>
      <li>Sensitive data encrypted at rest using AES-256</li>
      <li>Passwords stored as salted bcrypt hashes — never in plaintext</li>
      <li>Access controls and administrative logging in place</li>
    </ul>
    <p>While we implement industry-standard security, no system is completely secure. You use HoldOff at your own risk.</p>

    <hr>

    <h2>5. Your Privacy Rights &amp; Choices</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Access &amp; Portability:</strong> Request a copy of your data anytime via privacy@shouldiholdoff.live</li>
      <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Update account info in Settings</li>
      <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Delete your account in Settings or email us — most data removed within 90 days</li>
      <li><strong>Marketing Opt-Out:</strong> Unsubscribe from any email or update preferences in Settings</li>
      <li><strong>CCPA / GDPR:</strong> If you are a California or EU resident, you have additional rights including access, portability, erasure, and the right to object to processing</li>
    </ul>

    <hr>

    <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Active account: data retained while account is active</li>
      <li>Deleted account: most data deleted within 90 days</li>
      <li>Payment records: retained up to 7 years for legal/tax compliance</li>
      <li>Anonymized analytics: retained up to 24 months</li>
    </ul>

    <hr>

    <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>HoldOff is not intended for users under 18. We do not knowingly collect data from minors. If we become aware of such collection, we will delete the information immediately.</p>

    <hr>

    <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy as our practices or legal requirements change. We will notify you of material changes by email and by posting the updated policy on this page with a new "Last Updated" date.</p>

    <hr>

    <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@shouldiholdoff.live">privacy@shouldiholdoff.live</a></p>
    <p>We respond to privacy requests within 30 days or as required by law.</p>

